datasets = response.json()['result']['results']

datasets_w_geo = []
for d in datasets:
    if any(r['format'] in ['GeoJSON', 'SHP ZIP', 'GPKG', 'SHP'] for r in d['resources']):
        datasets_w_geo.append(d)
datasets_w_geo = [] for d in datasets: if any(r['format'] in ['GeoJSON', 'SHP ZIP', 'GPKG', 'SHP'] for r in d['resources']): datasets_w_geo.append(d)

h3 = pd.read_parquet(path / "h3-compact.parquet")

h3_gdf = cells_dataframe_to_geodataframe(
    pd.DataFrame({"cell": cells_parse(h3.h3_index)})
)
h3_gdf_reprojected = h3_gdf.to_crs(epsg=3857)
ax = h3_gdf_reprojected.plot(figsize=(10, 10), alpha=0.5, edgecolor="k")
cx.add_basemap(ax, source=cx.providers.CartoDB.Positron)
h3 = pd.read_parquet(path / "h3-compact.parquet") h3_gdf = cells_dataframe_to_geodataframe( pd.DataFrame({"cell": cells_parse(h3.h3_index)}) ) h3_gdf_reprojected = h3_gdf.to_crs(epsg=3857) ax = h3_gdf_reprojected.plot(figsize=(10, 10), alpha=0.5, edgecolor="k") cx.add_basemap(ax, source=cx.providers.CartoDB.Positron)
